#: index.docbook:724
msgid "Installation"
msgstr "Instalação"

#: index.docbook:726
msgid ""
"&kwuftpd; is part of the &kde; 2.0 base packages. It will automatically be "
"installed with your &kde; installation and requires &kde; 2.0 to function."
msgstr ""
"O &kwuftpd; faz parte dos pacotes de base do KDE 2.0. Será instalado com o "
"teu &kde; e necessita do &kde; 2.0 para funcionar."

#: index.docbook:730
msgid ""
"For more information, you should visit the &kde; website at <ulink "
"url=\"http://www.kde.org/\">http://www.kde.org</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Para mais informações, deves visitar o 'site' Web do &kde; em <ulink "
"url=\"http://www.kde.org/\">http://www.kde.org</ulink>."

#: index.docbook:733
msgid ""
"To obtain &kwuftpd; separately, it is part of the kdeadmin package, and "
"should be compiled and installed as indicated in the package's main "
"directory. New versions of kdeadmin can be obtained at <ulink "
"url=\"ftp://ftp.kde.org/pub/\">ftp://ftp.kde.org/pub/</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Para obteres o &kwuftpd; em separado, ele faz parte do pacote kdeadmin e "
"deve ser compilado e instalado tal como é indicado na directoria principal "
"do pacote. Podem ser obtidas as novas versões do kdeadmin em <ulink "
"url=\"ftp://ftp.kde.org/pub/\">ftp://ftp.kde.org/pub/</ulink>."

#: index.docbook:739
msgid "To build &kwuftpd;"
msgstr "Compilar o &kwuftpd;"

#: index.docbook:741
msgid ""
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput><command>cd</command> "
"<replaceable>kdeadmin/kwuftpd</replaceable></userinput>\n"
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput><command>./configure</command></userinput>\n"
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput><command>make</command></userinput>\n"
"Then as root:\n"
"<prompt>#</prompt> <userinput><command>make</command> "
"<option>install</option></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput><command>cd</command> "
"<replaceable>kdeadmin/kwuftpd</replaceable></userinput>\n"
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput><command>./configure</command></userinput>\n"
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput><command>make</command></userinput>\n"
"Depois como root:\n"
"<prompt>#</prompt> <userinput><command>make</command> "
"<option>install</option></userinput>"

#: index.docbook:749
msgid ""
"You also require an ftpd that can handle the generated ftpaccess files - "
"&kwuftpd; was written for <application>wu-ftpd</application> 2.6.1 (<ulink "
"url=\"ftp://ftp.wu-ftpd.org/pub/wu-ftpd/\">"
"ftp://ftp.wu-ftpd.org/pub/wu-ftpd/</ulink>) You can use the files with "
"<application>wu-ftpd</application> 2.5.0 as well, but don't expect all the "
"features to work."
msgstr ""
"Também precisas dum ftpd que possa tratar os ficheiros ftpaccess gerados - "
"o &kwuftpd; foi desenhado para o <application>wu-ftpd</application> 2.6.1 "
"(<ulink "
"url=\"ftp://ftp.wu-ftpd.org/pub/wu-ftpd/\">"
"ftp://ftp.wu-ftpd.org/pub/wu-ftpd/</ulink>) Podes também usar os ficheiros "
"com o <application>wu-ftpd</application> 2.5.0, mas não esperes que tudo "
"funcione."
